      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/23/13Monday, December 23, 2013 10:41 AM




Buck Sexton is in for Glenn and the #BuckDynasty is in full force.

  Buck talks the constant stream of lies coming from the Obama administration
     with the blatant lie of how the Healthcare Navigator site is working.

  Also, Susan Rice says that the NSA 
        "inadvertently made false representations" when discussing spying on Americans,
            which basically is fancy way of saying LIED.


  Plus, the Duck Dynasty media frenzy over the comments made in a GQ article
        and how Christian values are under attack.
